Mar 02 20:15:01 guest kojo-monitor[862015]: For each pair on each DEX:
Mar 02 20:15:01 guest kojo-monitor[862015]:     •    Fetch pool reserves via on-chain calls
Mar 02 20:15:01 guest kojo-monitor[862015]:     •    Compute spot price = reserveOut / reserveIn
